    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
    <description>Fontys Venlo best maven practices. "Up with your competencies"
        
        The 'Sebipom' Parent pom that provides all dependencies that you need for modern testing, generating 
        good looking Javadoc and a set of static test reports using spotbugs, pmd, and checkstyle.
        This is NOT cargo-cult, because NONE of the dependencies in this pom will end up in your final product.
    </description>

    <developers>
